{"tid":260743,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人早餐，一般港豬眼紅者勿入","createTime":"2017-05-28T00:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T06:24:34.000Z","uid":23412,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3ef381e4971bc21e210144dc26e299fab07c46","tid":260743,"uid":23412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T00:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/28/084755_4c965a7bf8f66e07f08ffd78f9aedf74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F084755_4c965a7bf8f66e07f08ffd78f9aedf74.jpg&h=b1808a62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個個都話呢間係三間之中 早餐最正<br />\n難得有機會試梗係試下<br />\n點知<br />\n呢份嘢已經變成40.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想起細個呢份嘢..18.5<br />\n由18.5加到20.5個一次 啲人嘈到幾大獲<br />\n而家慢慢變到40.5都冇乜人有大反應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港？不了"},{"pid":"759ef60e05c55b000429654ddffee8ed80ac578d","tid":260743,"uid":90791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T00:59:51.000Z","msg":"因為40.5黎講 真係好抵食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf6b4cc60a8176e470591247d2ee527953536ff","tid":260743,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20276d38ab2abebd40d21aa0181d6f6242a5fefc","tid":260743,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:12:58.000Z","msg":"肥到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好恐怖"},{"pid":"a2fe4472afcd162d9d617276b9361fc2682034b0","tid":260743,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好恐怖</blockquote><br />\n食一餐已經油、鹽、糖全部超過每日上限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdef04c4b20dcc8ce7dbc4ee681ca559f9f3c228",